Text.CultureInvariantString:
TAKING A BREAK FROM 
THE REVELRY, JOT NOTICED SOMETHING...

...A ROBED FIGURE STANDING NEAR THE 
ENTRANCE TO THE CASTLE

HE MADE HIS WAY OVER 
THERE TO INVESTIGATE
